## CHAPTER 3\
\
What It's Done to You\
\
# Experience: What It's Done to You\
\
In a classroom with rows of desks and a warm projector glow, You pause as projector hum brushes your attention. This moment feels weighted \'97 you fear that fumbling will define how others see them.\
\
Alright.\
\
You know where the sentence came from now.\
You know it made sense back then.\
You know why you've been running it for so long.\
