\cf10 \cb2 # Experience: Small Moves\cf0 \cb1 \
\
\cf10 \cb2 You don\'92t need a breakthrough.\cf0 \cb1 \
\
\cf10 \cb2 You need repetition.\cf0 \cb1 \
\
\cf10 \cb2 This chapter isn\'92t about doing something heroic.\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf10 \cb2 It\'92s about proving \'97 gently, repeatedly \'97 that movement is possible while anxiety is present.\cf0 \cb1 \
