\cf10 \cb2 That\'92s the check-in.\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf10 \cb2 Three seconds.\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf10 \cb2 No debate.\cf0 \cb1 \
\
\cf10 \cb2 ---\cf0 \cb1 \
\
\cf10 \cb2 ### Practice 2: Coherence Breathing (5 breaths per minute)\cf0 \cb1 \
\
\cf10 \cb2 Breathe in for 6 seconds.  \cf0 \cb1 \
\cf10 \cb2 Breathe out for 6 seconds.\cf0 \cb1 \
