\cf10 \cb2 This rhythm helps your system stay organized while you move.\cf0 \cb1 \
\
\cf10 \cb2 You\'92re not calming down.\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf10 \cb2 You\'92re stabilizing *while active*.\cf0 \cb1 \
