\
\cf10 \cb2 Continuation\cf0 \cb1 \
\
\cf10 \cb2 # Experience: Carrying It Forward\cf0 \cb1 \
\
\cf10 \cb2 There\'92s no finish line here.\cf0 \cb1 \
\
\cf10 \cb2 No moment where anxiety disappears forever.\cf0 \cb1 \
\
\cf10 \cb2 That was never the goal.\cf0 \cb1 \
\
\cf10 \cb2 ---\cf0 \cb1 \
\
\cf10 \cb2 ### Integration\cf0 \cb1 \
\
\cf10 \cb2 You learned:\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf10 \cb2 - Waiting wasn\'92t protecting you\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf10 \cb2 - Action was always possible\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf10 \cb2 - Anxiety didn\'92t decide your life\cf0 \cb1 \
\
\cf10 \cb2 Not because someone told you.\cf0 \cb1 \
\
\cf10 \cb2 Because you proved it.\cf0 \cb1 \
\
\cf10 \cb2 ---\cf0 \cb1 \
\
\cf10 \cb2 ### Reframe\cf0 \cb1 \
\
\cf10 \cb2 This isn\'92t a technique you apply.\cf0 \cb1 \
\
\cf10 \cb2 It\'92s a relationship you changed.\cf0 \cb1 \
\
\cf10 \cb2 ---\cf0 \cb1 \
\
\cf10 \cb2 ### Closing Identity\cf0 \cb1 \
\
\cf10 \cb2 You don\'92t wait for permission anymore.\cf0 \cb1 \
\
\cf10 \cb2 You move.\cf0 \cb1 \
\
\cf10 \cb2 Even when it\'92s uncomfortable.\cf0 \cb1 \
\
\cf10 \cb2 Especially then.\cf0 \cb1 \
\
\cf10 \cb2 ---\cf0 \cb1 \
\
\cf10 \cb2 ### Final Carry\cf0 \cb1 \
\
\cf10 \cb2 Nothing to maintain.\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf10 \cb2 Nothing to guard.\cf0 \cb1 \
\
\cf10 \cb2 Just continue.\cf0 \cb1 \
\
\cf10 \cb2 That\'92s enough.\cf0 \cb1 \
