### Practice 3: 4-7-8 Breathing\
\
Inhale 4.  \
Hold 7.  \
Exhale 8.\
\
This is for peak intensity moments.\
\
You're not waiting for the storm to pass.\
You're moving inside it.\
\
Practice for 3 rounds.\
