# Experience: Small Moves\
\
You know the theory. Now we practice. Small moves.\
\
### Practice 1: The 3-Second Check-In\
\
Pause.\
\
Where is the anxiety?\
Chest? Throat? Stomach?\
\
Ask one question only:\
\
**Danger \'97 or discomfort?**\
\
If it's discomfort, you proceed.\
\
That's the check-in.\
Three seconds.\
No debate.\
\
---\
\
### Practice 2: Coherence Breathing (5 breaths per minute)\
\
Breathe in for 6 seconds.  \
Breathe out for 6 seconds.\
\
Smooth. Continuous. No holding.\
\
This rhythm helps your system stay organized while you move.\
\
You're not calming down.\
You're stabilizing *while active*.\
\
\
Inhale for 4, exhale for 6. Repeat for 3-5 minutes.\
\
Practice for 5 minutes.\
